"tid":352244,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:41:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>都on9<br />\n只要機率唔係零<br />\n進行無限次trial總會有一次成功架<br />\n喱個世界好精巧根本唔係證明神既有效證據</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n幾年前TWITCH PLAY POKEMON就係想證實呢樣野"},{"pid":"8d52f50c008dd8c451dec746e7cc3cbb53f62f94","tid":352244,"uid":74315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:11:26.000Z","msg":"每一個生命 都有靈魂力量 <br />\n肉體只係盛載靈魂既工具<br />\n肉體死左之後 靈魂會回歸宇宙 循環不息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：9up"},{"pid":"e5dc00952189fc746adfddd806d5dd74cd30a6b1","tid":352244,"uid":74315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:13:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>輪迴有好多真實個案 但都研究跟進  好似印度呢個地方特別多的</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n輪迴解釋人口膨脹？</blockquote><br />\n果度話有多個平行宇宙， 如果生命守恆嘅話， 應該第二個世界減少緊生命， 加上好似無指定係人</blockquote><br />\n輪迴關人口膨脹咩事<br />\n人既上一世一定係人？<br />\n地球係宇宙靈魂既全部？"},{"pid":"7a5f9318f697240eae6c704c9371cb4928f4c032","tid":352244,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:17:17.000Z","msg":"全部鳩up<br />\n句句都話有試據顯示<br />\n但毛都冇條"},{"pid":"418c444f7a90c95f8c460c8588bf4c5f1912b0ff","tid":352244,"uid":130456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:19:58.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - 機界原種 )"},{"pid":"e7dc590a99472e45bff6095e320ad5c2d1758af2","tid":352244,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:37:31.000Z","msg":"醫生講物理都咁多連登仔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf68a0050cd3799325c8e29dcb09c9190ecbc7d9","tid":352244,"uid":63977,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:02:43.000Z","msg":"你係人, 因為你有意識<br />\n意識係人既大腦<br />\n受年齡/藥物影響會生長, 退化, 年老會忘記事情, 甚至連性格也會改變<br />\n所以已經可以肯定意識不能存活係另一個空間<br />\n<br />\n人就算有靈魂, 靈魂只是生命電池<br />\n人一死, 大腦就會死, 會失去原有大腦意識<br />\n失去了原有大腦意識, 其實靈魂下世做牛做馬又關你叉事<br />\n<br />\n基本上牛只有牛意識, 馬只有馬意識<br />\n你現在既意識只能活一世<br />\n靈魂就算可活千世萬<br />\n下一世已經唔係你<br />\n<br />\n就好似孖生咁, 一樣 DNA 又如何 ?<br />\n大腦唔同連性格也唔同"},{"pid":"1a40677efaf802efcf060c88d3ce6e937e89186e","tid":352244,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:17:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c638d61dd37f2272c59abcf2a5c400d4aaff90","tid":352244,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:49:09.000Z","msg":"咁就正 可以繼續供樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212b99ce21c51ea00c1af65d57ab843e6b9a9329","tid":352244,"uid":1633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:20:18.000Z","msg":"反而想知一直推上去 人&gt;外星人&gt;創做者&gt;上面係咩...真係我諗我死左都唔明，點解會有呢d所有野....."},{"pid":"e01517988d1a7856060ea5069482ef140c284249","tid":352244,"uid":35716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:27:13.000Z","msg":"從來唔信有鬼神......<br />\n完"},{"pid":"8465d84134ee6cf8b9090cc00be811e39bd73507","tid":352244,"uid":133256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:32:20.000Z","msg":"其實得意識不帶記憶，就算係真既都無乜用<br />\n到時都係所有野對於個意識既意義=無"},{"pid":"0f616bcae5bfa84ab237d36437379abbec3d0914","tid":352244,"uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:52:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每一個生命 都有靈魂力量 <br />\n肉體只係盛載靈魂既工具<br />\n肉體死左之後 靈魂會回歸宇宙 循環不息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：9up</blockquote><br />\n呢個係傳統西方認為嘅mind-body dualism 精神肉體二元論，但隨現今科學發展，應該趨向一元論，肉體靈魂係同一樣野，我覺得最好嘅理解方法係意識創造一切，包括物質，亦包括肉體，萬物本無相，色即是空。樓主文中講嗰本書叫Biocentrism，我睇過原文，但作者講嘅係宇宙唯心造，生物先係創造宇宙，有啲似佛學論述，但只係假說，唔係理論，因無法證實。"},{"pid":"9d4399e250a7cf53c963527b409a53a92efb5def","tid":352244,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:57:24.000Z","msg":"見到人名就可以負皮咗先"},{"pid":"5414ace71a94c8261dab3fb3b5fb2d18c87a534a","tid":352244,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T06:25:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b0247acd8fc03c61cc8ad42662cdc479c20546","tid":352244,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T09:06:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c70ffab2d4fc8a93d24ebc229bef2cb0563e95","tid":352244,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T09:31:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>輪迴有好多真實個案 但都研究跟進  好似印度呢個地方特別多的</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n輪迴解釋人口膨脹？</blockquote><br />\n果度話有多個平行宇宙， 如果生命守恆嘅話， 應該第二個世界減少緊生命， 加上好似無指定係人</blockquote><br />\n虛空有盡 眾生無盡"},{"pid":"62d8baa2fc307a426fab79b5e99425f77b21a238","tid":352244,"uid":3357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T12:18:41.000Z","msg":"如果意識係軟件 其實會唔會有方法可以搵第二個載體去保存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6958285aba3b9f6cae1f7848a7fafbc0199a5370","tid":352244,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T13:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da423977f42bf68efd7c9f3eeb13bba8ae8dcbe5","tid":352244,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T13:35:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果意識係軟件 其實會唔會有方法可以搵第二個載體去保存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSOMA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0727f64c355ebc8e9a29f49255e716fec60ba26","tid":352244,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T13:35:37.000Z","msg":"華文科學真係會睇壞腦"},{"pid":"a5eec5ce1b145dc7e6aa9ef0f77b12eef671b883","tid":352244,"uid":62950,"lik